    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 145</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 469</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate evocation <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can only be placed on melee weapons. A <em>mighty cleaving </em>weapon allows a wielder using the Cleave feat to make one additional attack if the first attack hits, as long as the next foe is adjacent to the first and also within reach. This additional attack cannot be against the first foe.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>divine power</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
